  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6269715/" class="title-link">纽伦堡中“爱与正义”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6269715"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1042441-29.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ygy8245/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">思郁</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-09-09"
      class="main-meta">2013-09-09 09:00:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6269715_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  纽伦堡，德国巴伐利亚州第二大城市，仅次于首府慕尼黑。我们能了解这个德国东南部的城市，一个主要原因就是，二战后从1945年11月到1946年10月期间，在这里举行了对纳粹战俘的审判，史称纽伦堡审判。  战后对纳粹战俘的审判，除了纽伦堡审判之外，我们还熟悉1961年在耶路撒冷对...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6269715/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">9有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6269715_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6269715_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6190976">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6190976/" class="title-link">正义永不食言</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6190976"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/74889304/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u74889304-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/74889304/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">花和尚</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-07-31"
      class="main-meta">2013-07-31 13:50:19</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6190976_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      人类文明的推进是否能够永远地消灭战争？至少在可预见的未来很长一段时间里，这仅仅是我们的期望。     可是，文明演进的伟大精神，是否能够消弭仇恨带来永无止境的报复？至少在20世纪最大的一场人类浩劫的余烬里，我们似乎看到了微弱的希望之光。 正义，是惩戒罪恶，是为...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6190976_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6190976_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










